snippet: The forward tore the anterior cruciate ligament in her left knee in Monday night’s game and will not be available to play in the Final Four.
lead_paragraph: The forward tore the anterior cruciate ligament in her left knee in Monday night’s game and will not be available to play in the Final Four.

headline.main: Notre Dame’s Natalie Achonwa to Miss Final Four With Knee Injury
headline.print_headline: Achonwa will miss Final Four with knee injury
